        <body>       
                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>10&#47;12&#47;85<lb/></p>
            <p>My dear Mr Morais<lb/></p>
            <p>I wrote to the Trustees<lb/> requesting an interview as to how<lb/> we can counteract <sic>Pittsburg</sic>&#45;&#45;<lb/> through the clerk&#39;s accident <del>it</del> my letter<lb/> was not read.  I have talked<lb/> with Mr Piza&#44; and I suggest to<lb/> him a call ;&#94; for a meeting of our congregation my father&#44; you<lb/> deSola &#40;Montreal&#41; and I to speak.<lb/> if possible delegations from these<lb/> congregations to be present&#59;<lb/></p>
            <p>A college is a big thing<del>t</del> and<lb/> I do not see where the professors<lb/> are to come from.<lb/></p>
            <p>Mr Piza will print your letter and extract<lb/> from your article in Record for circulation<lb/> <del>&#91;&#63;&#93;</del>  Among our congregation&#45;people.<lb/> But we should have a preliminary understanding<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>as to what scheme we can<lb/> elaborate to present to<lb/> such meeting.<lb/></p>
            <p>The date I suggest for the<lb/> mass meeting of my congregation<lb/> &#40;members a<hi rend="underline">nd seatholders</hi>&#41; and<lb/> those of yours etc that come<lb/> is 30 Dec. What say you&#63;&#45;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>Yrs<lb/>
                H Pereira Mendes<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
